#: software/templates/about_us.html:9
msgid ""
"wger helps you track your workouts, manage your nutrition, and reach your "
"fitness goals. We offer it as free, open-source software you can host "
"yourself, and also provide a convenient, free, and hosted version for easy "
"access."
