#: weight/templates/import_csv_form.html:18
msgid ""
"You can copy and paste from your spreadsheet into the text input,\n"
"the system will try to guess the format to import. The only things to "
"consider is\n"
"that the first column is the <strong>date</strong>, the second the "
"<strong>weight</strong>.\n"
"All further columns are ignored. There is a 1000 row limit.\n"
msgstr ""
"Du kan kopiere og lime inn ditt regneark i tekstfeltet,\n"
"systemet vil prøve å gjette format for å importere. Det eneste du bør "
"vurdere er\n"
"at den første kolonnen er <strong>dato</strong>, den andre er <strong>vekt</"
"strong>.\n"
"Alle ytterligere kolonner ignoreres. Det er en grense på 1000 rader.\n"

#: weight/templates/import_csv_form.html:24
msgid ""
"If there are errors, you can correct or discard them in a\n"
"second step."
msgstr ""
"Om det er feil, kan du korrigere eller ignorere de i\n"
"neste steg."

#: weight/templates/import_csv_preview.html:4
